node.text: Ive taken my bows. And my curtain calls. You’ve brought me fame and fortune andeverythingthatgoeswithit. I thank you all. But it’s been no bed of roses. No pleasure cruise. I consider it a challenge before the human race, and I’d never lose (and it goes on and on and on) WEEEEEEE ARE THE CHAMPIONS, MY FRIEEEEND. AND WE’LL KEEP ON FIGHTIIIIING TILL THE END. WE ARE THE CHAMPIONS, WE ARE THE CHAMPIOOOOONS, NOOOOO TIME FOR LOOOOSERS CAUSE WE WRE THE CHAMPIOOOOONS, OF THE WORLD

node.text: I’ve paid my dues. Time after time. I’ve done my sentence…but committed no crime. And bad mistakes - I’ve made a few.
